today we talked more about the advantages and disadvantages of social media, but in more detail this time. for example, we talked about linkedin and how that helps buisness people interact and help each other. But every silver lining has a cloud. Take linkedin as the same example again. Although it can show lots of positive things about you, people can comment about you and say things about you that may stop others from hiring you. The nwetalked about boundries for social media and how far you should go.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             

